entry.title: New Quarrel in Israel-Occupied West Bank: Where to Dump the Trash
entry.content: The territory’s more than 70 unofficial dumps send noxious fumes into Palestinian homes and sometimes kill farm animals.

entry.title: Ukrainian Forces Recapture Land Across Key River in South, Think Tank Says
entry.content: Kyiv’s forces have established a presence on the eastern bank of the Dnipro River in the southern Kherson region, according to the Institute for the Study of War, in what would be a significant step in Ukraine’s effort to reclaim occupied territory.

entry.title: Seattle Area to Vote on $1.2 Billion Tax Increase for Mental-Health System
entry.content: Local and state governments in the U.S. are looking for ways to address a shortage of resources.
